ygData.messageBody:
Salutations Ladies!

This made me think.
The other day I met a high level shadow night . . .
there is a kind of fun story there but I want go into
that now, but she said I could examine her stuff and
she had on a wedding ring of some kind (don't remember
the exact name). I asked about the ring and she said
it added 50 or 60 points to her health or something
like that. I honestly don't remember the exact details
but it was a big bonus.

Where would someone get such a thing or come by
something like that . . .

:o)
Brangvyne
